This is a word-isolated, speaker-dependent speech recognizor tool. This tools could recognize number word zero to ten and operator word: "plus", "minus","multiply","divide" said by a specific speaker.

ref.mlf: a macro file that contains all the labels of the test wav files. used by HResults.
recog.mlf: a macro file that contains all the recoginized label of the test wav files, generated by HVite.

